		全外教商务英语密集班
		 
		课程的设置主要针对日常的商务活动以及在不同场景下的商务会话,提高受训学员的商务沟通和交流能力。课程在深入现实商务活动中语言运用的同时，融入了更多的西方文化及管理方面的内容,它以一个全球化的思维角度去讨论企业的运作和发展。
		
		
		English365 is a three-level Business and general English 
		thpi2w.lq is designed for 
		learners who want to develop their English skills for their work and 
		their social and travel needs and therefore 
		reflects the work-life balance of busy working adults.
		
		
		It is particularly suitable for students who have studied English 
		in the past but need a new course to refresh, consolidate and practise 
		their existing English as well as learn a new language.
		
		Key features
		
 Stimulating content and activities. 
 Listening material based on authentic interviews with real 
		working people. 
 Various engaging and relevant topics offering excellent 
		speaking opportunities. 
 Survival language directly applicable to work and leisure 
		situations. 
 Focus on professional communication skills.
		
